{"id":"helkath","term":"Helkath","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Smoothness, a town of Asher, on the east border (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 19:25\">Josh. 19:25</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 21:31\">21:31</a>); called also Hukok (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 6:75\">1 Chr. 6:75</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Joshua 19:25","Joshua 21:31","1 Chronicles 6:75"]}